&lt;p&gt;Lustre: mdt01_020: service thread pid 682219 was inactive for 606.050 seconds. The thread might be hung, or it might only be slow and will resume later. Dumping the stack trace for debugging purposes:&lt;br/&gt;
Pid: 682219, comm: mdt01_020 5.4.0-1145-azure-fips #152+fips1-Ubuntu SMP Wed Jan 29 17:26:00 UTC 2025&lt;br/&gt;
Call Trace TBD:&lt;br/&gt;
