&lt;p&gt;Current suspicion is that the three especially huge directories (approaching 100M entries each) are causing directory entry thrashing, but that&apos;s speculative.&#160; The MDS nodes have &amp;gt;100GB of memory and are not near OOM.&#160; The stall with the high CPU usage lasts tens of minutes, but less than an hour.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Advice on further data collection to get or any tunables we can enable to help pinpoint the directory in question when this hits would be greatly appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
